abstract: >-
  BRAHM-AI is an India-first, Hindi-first, multilingual and multimodal
  artificial intelligence ecosystem combining voice interaction, computer
  vision, OCR, Sanskrit and Indian scripture intelligence, Panchang and
  Jyotish computation, retrieval-augmented generation, local language models,
  automation, agriculture intelligence, business AI agents, and planned
  developer APIs.

